 by Polbot]]\n\n\n{{Dipterocarpaceae-stub}}\n", "name_user": "WolfmanSF", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200etop:clean up", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hopea_mindanensis"}
